@startuml
title LowCortisol Platform - Support Backend Bounded Context Layers
left to right direction
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
hide circle

package "Support Backend Bounded Context" {
  class "Application" as Backend_support_Application <<layer>>
  class "Domain" as Backend_support_Domain <<layer>>
  class "Infrastructure" as Backend_support_Infrastructure <<layer>>
  class "Interfaces REST" as Backend_support_Interfaces_REST <<layer>>
}

Backend_support_Interfaces_REST ..> Backend_support_Application : commands / queries
Backend_support_Application ..> Backend_support_Domain : model and policies
Backend_support_Application ..> Backend_support_Infrastructure : repository ports / adapters
Backend_support_Infrastructure ..> Backend_support_Domain : persistence mapping
Backend_support_Interfaces_REST ..> Backend_support_Domain : resources from aggregates

note bottom of Backend_support_Application
Detailed class diagrams for each layer are available in docs/diagrams/class/backend/layers/support.
end note

@enduml
